DOC.brief_summary: The health-related quality of life questionnaire "EQ-5D" has been collected in connection with several interventional and observational studies where the no-touch vein harvesting technique in CABG has been used. The results of the questionnaires will be compiled and reported in this study.
DOC.brief_title: Graft Patency as a Predictor of Health-related Quality of Life.
DOC.criteria: 1. Operated at our department for a coronary artery bypass surgery with either the notouch harvesting technique of conventional harvesting technique. 2. Completed the EQ5D questionnaire. 3. Signed and dated consent. 1. Substantial missing data from the EQ5D questionnaire. 2. Unable to comprehend the different inquiries in the questionnaire.
